text: Lena Kathren Headey ( ; born 3 October 1973) is an English actress. She starred in the Home Box Office television series Game of Thrones and the Fox Television Network television series Terminator: The Sarah Connor Chronicles. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:English movie actors Category:English television actors Category:English voice actors Category:English stage actors Category:Actors from Yorkshire
